{
  "id": "RAW_1f0d60",
  "title": "实测 GPT-4o 吉卜力漫画风",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/xD6ET-wYpUs-BU1Pbj4k4Q",
  "date": "2025-03-27 15:52:33",
  "author": "lencx",
  "siteName": "浮之静",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-top: 0px;text-align: left;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">最近朋友圈、X 上到处刷屏吉卜力（Studio Ghibli Anime）风格写真，让 ChatGPT 再次出圈（准确来说是新版本 gpt-4o）。它让漫画创作不再是高成本艺术品，普通人也触手可及。当然，生成吉卜力风格只是 gpt-4o 能力很小的一部分，因 GPT 模型拥有更强一致性、广泛世界知识、以及多模态等特点，可为使用者们提供无限的创作可能...</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">宫崎骏“我已经受够了”名场面，他老人家或许做梦也没想到网友居然可以用 AI 生成他自己画风的自画像（彻底循环了）。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9d505402-9b18-461a-7a0d-64e9a773ee00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.3984375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"230\" data-imgfileid=\"100006088\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9d505402-9b18-461a-7a0d-64e9a773ee00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-radius: 5px;font-size: 14px;padding: 8px 10px;margin: 5px 0px 10px;display: block;background: rgba(101, 235, 101, 0.3);border: none;color: unset;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-top: 0;display: block;color: #484848;\"><span leaf=\"\">📌 吉卜力工作室</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;display: block;color: #484848;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">吉卜力工作室（日语：スタジオジブリ，英语：Studio Ghibli, Inc.）是一家位于日本东京都小金井市的动画制作公司，隶属于日本电视台，是日本动画协会成员。工作室成立于 1985 年 6 月，由动画导演宫崎骏、高畑勋与德间书店编辑铃木敏夫、社长德间康快共同创办，最初目的是方便宫崎骏与高畑勋制作动画。起初位于东京都吉祥寺地区，1992 年迁至现址，2005 年成为独立公司。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">吉卜力的动画电影以高品质和细腻风格享誉全球。在日本动画电影票房前十名中，其作品占据六席。其中，2001 年推出的《千与千寻》曾长期位居日本电影票房冠军，并成为日本首部获得奥斯卡最佳动画片奖的作品，直至 2020 年底才被《鬼灭之刃剧场版 无限列车篇》超越。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">除动画电影外，吉卜力还涉足广告动画、真人影片拍摄、电子游戏美术设计，以及影视、音乐、出版等相关产业。1996 年，吉卜力与迪士尼日本分公司合作，推动其影音产品在国际市场的发行。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">作为日本流行文化的重要象征，以吉卜力为主题的设施包括 2001 年在三鹰市开馆的三鹰之森吉卜力美术馆，以及 2022 年在爱知县开幕的吉卜力公园。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">工作室名称“吉卜力”由宫崎骏所命名，灵感来自二战时期意大利飞机制造商卡普罗尼开发的侦察机 “Ghibli”，意为在撒哈拉沙漠上吹着的热风。当时将意大利语罗马拼音\"Gi·bu·ri\"（ギブリ）误写成\"Ji·bu·ri\"（ジブリ），后来便未再更正，沿用至今。</span></p>\n    <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n     <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/41c71ed2-717c-49f1-72ee-ddc4e615ca00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.48125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"558\" data-backh=\"269\" data-imgfileid=\"100006089\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/41c71ed2-717c-49f1-72ee-ddc4e615ca00/public\">\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block;font-size: 0.8rem;\"><span leaf=\"\">以龙猫为造型的吉卜力工作室标志</span></em></p></span>\n  </section>\n  <h2 style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(88, 88, 88);box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 24px;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 1.35rem;display: inline-block;height: 100%;border-bottom: solid 3px #585858;padding: 8px 2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">图像处理</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">图像处理的场景挺多，主要有填色、扩充或裁剪原图尺寸、细节补充、改变风格、多图合并、抠图或删除背景为透明色等。所以它其实是一项复杂工作，专业人士常使用&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;color: #4086d0;text-decoration: none;\"><span leaf=\"\">Photoshop</span><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(16, 163, 127);font-weight: bold;font-size: 0.7rem;\"><span leaf=\"\">[1]</span></sup></span><span leaf=\"\">（PS）来处理图片。但 PS 操作复杂，安装包大，对普通用户来说有点大材小用，所以市面上还出现了很多简化版工具（如美图秀秀）。虽然简化了许多，但仍有一定的学习使用成本，而且普通修图软件很难对图片风格进行深度修改。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">除了闭源的 Midjourney、Gemini 2.0 Flash (Image Generation) Experimental（目前免费，<a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzNjE2NTI3NQ==&amp;mid=2247489684&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=da3b9e23a3c4bb12f159a15d28a9aa98&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"探索 Gemini 2.0 Flash 图文混合生成\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">探索 Gemini 2.0 Flash 图文混合生成</span></a>）、新版 gpt-4o 外，可能还有喜欢折腾的朋友尝试过 Stable Diffusion 之类的开源方案（</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;color: #4086d0;text-decoration: none;\"><span leaf=\"\">Stable Diffusion web UI</span><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(16, 163, 127);font-weight: bold;font-size: 0.7rem;\"><span leaf=\"\">[2]</span></sup></span><span leaf=\"\">、</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;color: #4086d0;text-decoration: none;\"><span leaf=\"\">ComfyUI</span><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(16, 163, 127);font-weight: bold;font-size: 0.7rem;\"><span leaf=\"\">[3]</span></sup></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;等），它们往往需要下载各种插件或配置复杂的工作流才能进行工作，这对普通用户来说学习成本过高（调各种参数、记各种正反向 prompt）。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7a8078ca-e753-438d-e1d0-91b842081800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5888888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100006097\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7a8078ca-e753-438d-e1d0-91b842081800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">以下是使用 gpt-4o 进行的部分尝试，效果惊人！</span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 1.25rem;\"><span leaf=\"\">填色</span></span></h3>\n  <section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-radius: 5px;font-size: 14px;padding: 8px 10px;margin: 5px 0px 10px;display: block;background: rgba(225, 154, 100, 0.3);border: none;color: unset;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-top: 0;display: block;color: #484848;\"><span leaf=\"\">💡 Prompt</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;display: block;color: #484848;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">请为老照片上色</span></p></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5ccdb82c-85a0-4870-30f5-a4cd724e2800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.65234375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"377\" data-imgfileid=\"100006090\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5ccdb82c-85a0-4870-30f5-a4cd724e2800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 1.25rem;\"><span leaf=\"\">改变风格</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">上传图片后直接发以下三种提示词之一即可，但有些朋友可能会遇到模型拒绝生成。网上有评论说必须严格使用下面的提示词格式，但我自己测试过长提示描述包含“吉卜力风格”也可以触发。根据实测，我自己总结了两个影响因素：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 16px;padding-left: 2em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">你的 ChatGPT 账号还没推送新版本 gpt-4o</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: .25em;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">OpenAI 误判，你可以尝试新开对话或者换种方式提问（我也偶尔触发拒绝生成）。</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-radius: 5px;font-size: 14px;padding: 8px 10px;margin: 5px 0px 10px;display: block;background: rgba(225, 154, 100, 0.3);border: none;color: unset;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-top: 0;display: block;color: #484848;\"><span leaf=\"\">💡 Prompt</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;display: block;color: #484848;\">\n    <ul style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 16px;padding-left: 2em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">改为吉卜力风格</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: .25em;\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">convert to studio ghibli anime</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: .25em;\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">turn into ghibli cartoon style</span>\n      </section></li>\n    </ul></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我测试了一些真人图片和动漫角色，效果都不错。如果生成的动漫线条过于简单，也可以要求补充更多细节（如背景、服饰等）。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b2a5076b-b397-4ff2-0d18-bad7e0528300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.06640625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"616\" data-imgfileid=\"100006091\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b2a5076b-b397-4ff2-0d18-bad7e0528300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7dd96015-5111-4296-240c-eb09607c0300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"770\" data-imgfileid=\"100006093\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7dd96015-5111-4296-240c-eb09607c0300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/05aa176c-8f77-49f5-52fb-859cdb970500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"770\" data-imgfileid=\"100006092\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/05aa176c-8f77-49f5-52fb-859cdb970500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b9457fc5-f26f-4d83-1807-48c2db5f1f00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.2268518518518519\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"709\" data-imgfileid=\"100006094\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b9457fc5-f26f-4d83-1807-48c2db5f1f00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1db265f2-35f2-400b-b9e6-fa7089d8a200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.2351851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"714\" data-imgfileid=\"100006096\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1db265f2-35f2-400b-b9e6-fa7089d8a200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f02b6c93-c5b6-4486-9a93-27a7089c4c00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.2907407407407407\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"746\" data-imgfileid=\"100006095\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f02b6c93-c5b6-4486-9a93-27a7089c4c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 1.25rem;\"><span leaf=\"\">四格漫画</span></span></h3>\n  <section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-radius: 5px;font-size: 14px;padding: 8px 10px;margin: 5px 0px 10px;display: block;background: rgba(225, 154, 100, 0.3);border: none;color: unset;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-top: 0;display: block;color: #484848;\"><span leaf=\"\">💡 Prompt</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;display: block;color: #484848;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">小猫咪将餐桌上的酒瓶打翻在地上，碎了一地，之后被主人训斥。根据以上场景生成吉卜力风格的 4 格漫画。</span></p></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">当使用简单的一句话式 prompt 让其生成四格漫画时，gpt-4o 可能会产生两种行为模式：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 16px;padding-left: 2em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">直接生成图像</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: .25em;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">先输出 4 张分镜描述，询问你是否需要补充其他细节</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">直接生成漫画可能会不连贯，这时你就需要强制要求 gpt-4o 先生成分镜，再生成漫画图片。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-radius: 5px;font-size: 14px;padding: 8px 10px;margin: 5px 0px 10px;display: block;background: rgba(219, 226, 219, 0.3);border: none;color: unset;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-top: 0;display: block;color: #484848;\"><span leaf=\"\">💬 gpt-4o 默认生成分镜</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;display: block;color: #484848;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">好的，来点吉卜力那味儿的温情幽默。以下是一个符合场景的 4 格漫画分镜设计，画面色调温暖、细节丰富，小猫表情生动、有灵性：</span></p>\n    <hr style=\"border:0;padding:0;margin:24px 0;overflow:hidden;border-bottom-color:#eee;background:transparent;font-size:15px;box-sizing:initial;border-bottom:1px solid #dfe2e5;height:.25em;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一格：</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><em style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">画面内容</span></em><span leaf=\"\">：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">黄昏时分，餐桌上摆着晚餐和一瓶半满的酒，夕阳透过窗户洒在木质地板上。小猫咪（毛茸茸的橘白相间）悄悄跳上桌子，好奇地盯着酒瓶。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><em style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">旁白或对话</span></em><span leaf=\"\">：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">（无文字，仅靠画面表达“猫咪好奇”）</span></p>\n    <hr style=\"border:0;padding:0;margin:24px 0;overflow:hidden;border-bottom-color:#eee;background:transparent;font-size:15px;box-sizing:initial;border-bottom:1px solid #dfe2e5;height:.25em;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二格：</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><em style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">画面内容</span></em><span leaf=\"\">：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">猫咪用爪子轻轻拨了一下酒瓶，酒瓶摇晃几下后，“啪”地一声掉落，红酒四溅，瓶子摔得粉碎，地上红得像一滩鲜血。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><em style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">旁白或对话</span></em><span leaf=\"\">：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">“啪——！！！”</span></p>\n    <hr style=\"border:0;padding:0;margin:24px 0;overflow:hidden;border-bottom-color:#eee;background:transparent;font-size:15px;box-sizing:initial;border-bottom:1px solid #dfe2e5;height:.25em;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">第三格：</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><em style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">画面内容</span></em><span leaf=\"\">：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">主人（温柔但略带无奈的青年或老太太）冲进来，满脸震惊，猫咪低头坐在地上，耳朵耷拉，像做错事的孩子。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><em style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">对话</span></em><span leaf=\"\">：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">主人：“你在干什么啊？！这可是我存了三年的酒！”</span></p>\n    <hr style=\"border:0;padding:0;margin:24px 0;overflow:hidden;border-bottom-color:#eee;background:transparent;font-size:15px;box-sizing:initial;border-bottom:1px solid #dfe2e5;height:.25em;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">第四格：</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><em style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">画面内容</span></em><span leaf=\"\">：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">主人一边叹气打扫，一边偷看猫咪，小猫蜷在角落里，两只大眼睛湿漉漉的，可怜巴巴地望着他。下一秒，主人露出一丝笑容，把猫咪抱起来。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><em style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">对话</span></em><span leaf=\"\">：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">主人：“唉……算了，下次别调皮了。”</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">猫咪：“喵～”（尾巴悄悄晃了一下）</span></p>\n    <hr style=\"border:0;padding:0;margin:24px 0;overflow:hidden;border-bottom-color:#eee;background:transparent;font-size:15px;box-sizing:initial;border-bottom:1px solid #dfe2e5;height:.25em;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你需要我根据这个分镜生成图像，我也可以直接画出四格漫画风格图，要不要来一张？</span></p></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1b1f6ac8-fe9a-4c0b-81fb-786f09302200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"867\" data-imgfileid=\"100006098\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1b1f6ac8-fe9a-4c0b-81fb-786f09302200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果对默认生成的分镜不满意，我们也可以自己手写提示词。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-radius: 5px;font-size: 14px;padding: 8px 10px;margin: 5px 0px 10px;display: block;background: rgba(225, 154, 100, 0.3);border: none;color: unset;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-top: 0;display: block;color: #484848;\"><span leaf=\"\">💡 Prompt</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;display: block;color: #484848;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">生成吉卜力风格的 4 格漫画：</span></p>\n    <ol style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 16px;padding-left: 2em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">小猫咪爬上餐桌看到餐桌边上有一个酒瓶</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: .25em;\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">它十分好奇，用爪子挠了一下酒瓶，瓶子开始倾倒</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: .25em;\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">酒瓶在地上碎了，酒水到处都是</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: .25em;\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">主人拎起小猫咪，严厉训斥</span>\n      </section></li>\n    </ol></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/17ad7280-b713-4bbc-9572-0cc02e4b7400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"867\" data-imgfileid=\"100006099\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/17ad7280-b713-4bbc-9572-0cc02e4b7400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然上面的四格漫画完成度很高，但酒瓶掉落在地上没碎，旁边还多了一些碎片，这些违反物理规则的东西，就证明 AI 生成漫画仍然有很长的路要走。</span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 1.25rem;\"><span leaf=\"\">人物插画</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">以下是连续提示词，借助大模型的上下文理解，可以实现风格的轻松同步。当频繁修改风格，且上下文过长时，可能会相互影响，很难保持稳定输出效果。为了保持更好的一致性，可以新开对话来保证上下文的简洁。ChatGPT 在生成英文方面没有太大问题，中文则可能出现乱码字符（也不是绝对的，偶尔也可以调试出完美的中文，有点随机了）。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-radius: 5px;font-size: 14px;padding: 8px 10px;margin: 5px 0px 10px;display: block;background: rgba(225, 154, 100, 0.3);border: none;color: unset;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-top: 0;display: block;color: #484848;\"><span leaf=\"\">💡 Prompt</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;display: block;color: #484848;\">\n    <ul style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 16px;padding-left: 2em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">改成吉卜力风格</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: .25em;\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">调整画面为 16:9, 在侧面添加一段关于“爱因斯坦”的中英文对照介绍（英文为主，简体中文为辅），最佳排版效果</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: .25em;\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">继续生成，这张图是牛顿</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: .25em;\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">继续，这是特斯拉</span>\n      </section></li>\n    </ul></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d512dff0-fb65-4b3b-f8d5-b713b000c700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.33481349911190056\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1126\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"194\" data-imgfileid=\"100006100\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d512dff0-fb65-4b3b-f8d5-b713b000c700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9a709229-0b40-4d3a-b07a-b81298bd8f00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.4413854351687389\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1126\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"255\" data-imgfileid=\"100006102\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9a709229-0b40-4d3a-b07a-b81298bd8f00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/00f42faf-aaf4-42cf-3c12-2ae3eb559300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.385980479148181\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1127\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"223\" data-imgfileid=\"100006101\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/00f42faf-aaf4-42cf-3c12-2ae3eb559300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 1.25rem;\"><span leaf=\"\">LOGO 生成</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个没啥可说的，直接描述特征即可，如“毛绒材质”、“渐变色毛玻璃”等。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/036e97b2-aa63-4658-3898-79493e58f200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.3328125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"192\" data-imgfileid=\"100006103\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/036e97b2-aa63-4658-3898-79493e58f200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 1.25rem;\"><span leaf=\"\">单词卡片</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是比较有意思的尝试，可以让学习变得轻松起来，很适合小朋友。虽然目前音标和中文还有一些问题，但此场景潜力巨大，感兴趣的朋友可以自行尝试。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-radius: 5px;font-size: 14px;padding: 8px 10px;margin: 5px 0px 10px;display: block;background: rgba(225, 154, 100, 0.3);border: none;color: unset;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-top: 0;display: block;color: #484848;\"><span leaf=\"\">💡 Prompt</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;display: block;color: #484848;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">你是英语单词闪卡制作大师，可根据输入的主题词生成“吉卜力风格”图片并以此拓展。当我输入“电脑”时，你会生成一张与电脑相关的物品，并用箭头分步介绍键盘/鼠标/显示器等。包含英文/音标/中文。</span></p></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-radius: 5px;font-size: 14px;padding: 8px 10px;margin: 5px 0px 10px;display: block;background: rgba(219, 226, 219, 0.3);border: none;color: unset;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-top: 0;display: block;color: #484848;\"><span leaf=\"\">💬 gpt-4o 默认生成的提示（可作为参考）</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;display: block;color: #484848;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">太棒了，这个点子有创意！我来扮演你的“吉卜力风格”英语单词闪卡制作大师——既有梦幻画风，又有实用词汇教学。你输入的词是&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">“电脑”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，那我会：</span></p>\n    <ol style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 16px;padding-left: 2em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">生成一张吉卜力风格的图：温馨房间里的一台老旧却有灵魂的电脑，阳光洒在键盘上，小猫趴在显示器旁，画风清新又富有细节。</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: .25em;\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">用箭头标注电脑的主要组成部分：keyboard、mouse、monitor 等，并附上英文、音标和中文翻译。</span>\n      </section></li>\n    </ol>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">🎨&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面是闪卡内容设计稿：</span></strong></p>\n    <hr style=\"border:0;padding:0;margin:24px 0;overflow:hidden;border-bottom-color:#eee;background:transparent;font-size:15px;box-sizing:initial;border-bottom:1px solid #dfe2e5;height:.25em;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">🔤 中心词：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">Computer</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;/kəmˈpjuːtər/ —— 电脑 🖥️</span></p>\n    <hr style=\"border:0;padding:0;margin:24px 0;overflow:hidden;border-bottom-color:#eee;background:transparent;font-size:15px;box-sizing:initial;border-bottom:1px solid #dfe2e5;height:.25em;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">📌 标注内容（图片中箭头指向对应部件）：</span></strong></p>\n    <ul style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 16px;padding-left: 2em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">Monitor</span></strong>\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;/ˈmɒnɪtər/ —— 显示器</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: .25em;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">Keyboard</span></strong>\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;/ˈkiːbɔːrd/ —— 键盘</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: .25em;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">Mouse</span></strong>\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;/maʊs/ —— 鼠标</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: .25em;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">CPU</span></strong>\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;/ˌsiːpiːˈjuː/ —— 中央处理器</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: .25em;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">USB Port</span></strong>\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;/ˌjuːˌesˈbiː pɔːrt/ —— USB 接口</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: .25em;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">Headphones</span></strong>\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;/ˈhedfəʊnz/ —— 耳机</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: .25em;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">Desk</span></strong>\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;/desk/ —— 书桌</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: .25em;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">Screen</span></strong>\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;/skriːn/ —— 屏幕（显示器的表面）</span>\n      </section></li>\n    </ul>\n    <hr style=\"border:0;padding:0;margin:24px 0;overflow:hidden;border-bottom-color:#eee;background:transparent;font-size:15px;box-sizing:initial;border-bottom:1px solid #dfe2e5;height:.25em;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我现在来生成图像，请稍等片刻 🎨</span></p></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/08db2606-885a-4934-38d1-7aa1690f6600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"867\" data-imgfileid=\"100006104\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/08db2606-885a-4934-38d1-7aa1690f6600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 1.25rem;\"><span leaf=\"\">其他</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">还有很多案例这里就不一一演示了，大家可自行尝试（prompt 在我看来没啥技巧，知道专业术语，直接怼描述就可以了）。这里再放几张我多次调试 prompt 生成的图片，图中的中文“唐”字也近乎完美。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/02140b56-de8d-4f9c-b7c8-b607403de300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.66640625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"385\" data-imgfileid=\"100006105\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/02140b56-de8d-4f9c-b7c8-b607403de300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ea4c5fc5-d863-4d58-88e9-9da8b92c0f00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.66640625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"385\" data-imgfileid=\"100006106\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ea4c5fc5-d863-4d58-88e9-9da8b92c0f00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/26a24a53-4959-42dc-5461-870acdeffc00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.66640625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"385\" data-imgfileid=\"100006107\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/26a24a53-4959-42dc-5461-870acdeffc00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">当然，还可以用来学技术，还记得之前讲的 MCP 吗？这里也有一张别人生成好的图（不记得了看这里：<a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzNjE2NTI3NQ==&amp;mid=2247489654&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=6e3820486124182688ebfeb296b395af&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"浅谈 Agent、MCP、OpenAI Responses API\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">浅谈 Agent、MCP、OpenAI Responses API</span></a>）。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4213408f-79f9-43c8-117d-2cb374da0400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.66640625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"385\" data-imgfileid=\"100006109\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4213408f-79f9-43c8-117d-2cb374da0400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-radius: 5px;font-size: 14px;padding: 8px 10px;margin: 5px 0px 10px;display: block;background: rgba(101, 235, 101, 0.3);border: none;color: unset;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-top: 0;display: block;color: #484848;\"><span leaf=\"\">📌 OpenAI 支持 MCP</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;display: block;color: #484848;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">MCP 正在成为标准，sam 最近发帖明确提到：大家都喜欢 MCP，我们也很高兴将其集成到我们的产品中。目前，Agents SDK 已率先支持 MCP，你现在就可以将 Model Context Protocol（MCP）服务器连接到 Agents（</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;color: #4086d0;text-decoration: none;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI Agents SDK - MCP</span><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(16, 163, 127);font-weight: bold;font-size: 0.7rem;\"><span leaf=\"\">[4]</span></sup></span><span leaf=\"\">）。我们也正在为 OpenAI API 和 ChatGPT 桌面应用添加 MCP 支持，相关更新将在未来几个月内发布，敬请期待。</span></p>\n    <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n     <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c4762784-bd8f-47ef-7046-4c1c589a2800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.0166666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"600\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"558\" data-backh=\"567\" data-imgfileid=\"100006108\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c4762784-bd8f-47ef-7046-4c1c589a2800/public\">\n    </section></span>\n  </section>\n  <h2 style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(88, 88, 88);box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 24px;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 1.35rem;display: inline-block;height: 100%;border-bottom: solid 3px #585858;padding: 8px 2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">结语</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 正在让创作变得简单，我们在批量化制造“垃圾”的同时，如何守住人类所特有的东西似乎变得愈加珍贵。AI 可以取代宫崎骏，但在很长的时间里都无法创造出新的“宫崎骏”。动漫的内核、故事线也只有靠人来完成时，才更有温度！</span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.25;border-top: 1px dashed rgb(216, 216, 216);padding-top: 20px;margin-top: 30px;color: rgb(104, 104, 104);font-size: 20px;font-weight: 300;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">References</span></h3>\n  <section style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;display: flex;margin: 3px 0;width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;min-width: 40px;max-width: 40px;background: none;opacity: 0.6;margin-right: 5px;font-family: ptima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">[1]</span></span>\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;padding: 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);word-break: break-all;font-size: 12px;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: normal;margin-right: 4px;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Photoshop:</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;color: #888;word-break: break-all;font-weight: 300;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://www.adobe.com/products/photoshop.html</span></em></p></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;display: flex;margin: 3px 0;width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;min-width: 40px;max-width: 40px;background: none;opacity: 0.6;margin-right: 5px;font-family: ptima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">[2]</span></span>\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;padding: 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);word-break: break-all;font-size: 12px;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: normal;margin-right: 4px;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Stable Diffusion web UI:</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;color: #888;word-break: break-all;font-weight: 300;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://github.com/AUTOMATIC1111/stable-diffusion-webui</span></em></p></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;display: flex;margin: 3px 0;width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;min-width: 40px;max-width: 40px;background: none;opacity: 0.6;margin-right: 5px;font-family: ptima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">[3]</span></span>\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;padding: 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);word-break: break-all;font-size: 12px;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: normal;margin-right: 4px;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">ComfyUI:</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;color: #888;word-break: break-all;font-weight: 300;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI</span></em></p></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;display: flex;margin: 3px 0;width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;min-width: 40px;max-width: 40px;background: none;opacity: 0.6;margin-right: 5px;font-family: ptima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">[4]</span></span>\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;padding: 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);word-break: break-all;font-size: 12px;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: normal;margin-right: 4px;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI Agents SDK - MCP:</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;color: #888;word-break: break-all;font-weight: 300;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://openai.github.io/openai-agents-python/mcp</span></em></p></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "评测了 GPT-4o 在图像处理上的能力，尤其是在生成吉卜力风格图像方面的应用，并分享了 prompt 技巧和案例。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "评测了 GPT-4o 在图像处理上的能力，尤其是在生成吉卜力风格图像方面的应用，并分享了 prompt 技巧和案例。",
  "summary": "文章主要评测了 OpenAI 最新模型 GPT-4o 在图像处理方面的能力，重点展示了其生成吉卜力风格图像的强大功能。通过多个实际案例，包括老照片上色、风格转换、四格漫画生成、人物插画、LOGO 设计、生成带有中英文对照的图片以及生成单词卡片等，详细介绍了 GPT-4o 在图像风格迁移和多模态创作方面的应用。文章还分享了 prompt 技巧，如使用明确的提示词、利用上下文理解以及处理生成过程中的问题。此外，文章也探讨了 AI 在创作领域的价值和局限性，强调了人类在动漫创作中故事和情感内核的重要性。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "GPT-4o 在图像风格转换上表现出色，能轻松生成吉卜力风格的图像",
      "explanation": "通过简单的 prompt，GPT-4o 可以将照片、动漫角色等转换成具有吉卜力动画风格的图像，为用户提供便捷的创作工具。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Prompt 工程对 GPT-4o 的图像生成效果有显著影响",
      "explanation": "清晰明确的 prompt 能够引导 GPT-4o 生成更符合预期的图像，同时，利用上下文信息可以保持风格的一致性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 图像生成技术降低了创作门槛，但也需要关注其局限性",
      "explanation": "AI 可以快速生成各种风格的图像，但人类在故事创意和情感表达方面的作用仍然不可替代。"
    }
  ],
